# Customer Churn Analytics Dashboard
# Requirements

## Power BI Desktop
Version: 2.0 or later (free download)
Download: https://powerbi.microsoft.com/desktop/

## No additional Python or package dependencies required
## Dashboard is entirely built within Power BI Desktop using:
# - Power Query (M language) for data transformation
# - DAX for measures and calculated columns
# - Power BI visualisations (no custom visuals required)
